  "description": "<p>\n\t<a href=\"http://st.hujiang.com/topic/166838881967/\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>口语评分系统全新上线！！点我去评分&gt;&gt;</strong></a></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><img src=\"http://i3.s.7.hjfile.cn/entry/201511/4141788a-2d1a-4b95-b4dd-d030e192b3a7.jpg\" />最近沪江英语有一篇文章火了《</span><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p753565/\" style=\"font-size: 16px;\" target=\"_blank\">胡歌获奖英文演讲惊艳：哪些明星口语爆好？</a><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">》看到胡歌、汤唯、吴彦祖等颜值爆表的明星，讲着一口燃到爆的流利口语，你是不是不禁想问：</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(149, 55, 52);\"><strong>到底如何才能把口语练好呢？</strong></span></p>\n<p>\n\t&nbsp;</p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; color: rgb(149, 55, 52);\"><strong>提升口语最重要的一条基本原则是：在发音标准的基础上&mdash;&mdash;输入决定输出，多练决定熟练。</strong></span>大量的阅读和听力输入是有效提升口语的前提，模仿英美剧或与母语人士交流可以让口语出神入化。</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-size: 16.3636360168457px;\"><img src=\"http://i3.s.7.hjfile.cn/entry/201511/b58274d0-06b1-42d6-ae87-588a59829ac8.jpg\" /></span></p>\n<p>\n\t&nbsp;</p>\n<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://i3.s.7.hjfile.cn/entry/201511/722aedbd-50be-49d3-8c63-463ebd820dea.jpg\" /><span style=\"font-size: 16.3636360168457px;\">英语的母语人士更容易接受外国人在对话中的语法错误，而不易接受难懂的、勉强听明白的糟糕的发音。也就是说，发音有问题会严重地影响正常的交流。</span></p>\n<p>\n\t<span style=\"font-size: 16.3636360168457px;\"><br />\n\t</span></p>\n<p style=\"font-size: 16.3636360168457px; white-space: normal;\">\n\t<span style=\"font-size: 16.3636360168457px;\">反过来讲，如果你练就了优美的英文发音，母语人士将更乐于与你交流，他们听你能把他们的母语说得那么漂亮一定会大加赞赏！这又将进一步加深你对这一语言的喜好，此乃一个良性循环的过程。</span></p>\n<p style=\"font-size: 16.3636360168457px; white-space: normal;\">\n\t<span style=\"font-size: 16.3636360168457px;\"><br />\n\t</span></p>\n<p style=\"font-size: 16.3636360168457px; white-space: normal;\">\n\t<span style=\"color: rgb(31, 73, 125);\"><strong>所以说，发音是练好英语口语的基础。</strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"font-size: 16.3636360168457px; white-space: normal;\">\n\t&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"font-size: 16.3636360168457px; white-space: normal;\">\n\t想练就标准扎实的发音，你可以去<a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/lingjichu/\" target=\"_blank\">英语零基础入门</a>的字母音标模块学习跟读48个国际音标，这个频道使用起来非常方便、点击按钮就可以自动发音，还可以去<a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/zt/yingbiaofayin/\" target=\"_blank\">英语音标</a>专题看一些发音的宝贵经验。<a href=\"http://class.hujiang.com/classzt/MKTTopic_p90996?ch_source=ipo_en_0_rw&amp;editorid=29de7a73\" target=\"_blank\"><strong>12.12学习趴</strong></a><strong>中</strong>，口语课程全额奖学金等着你！</p>\n<p style=\"font-size: 16.3636360168457px; white-space: normal;\">\n\t&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"font-size: 16.3636360168457px; white-space: normal;\">\n\t如果你觉得自己一个人学习太单调，想找些小伙伴一起练发音，那么推荐以下活动给你：</p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft Yahei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', sans-serif; font-size: 16.3636360168457px; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal;\">\n\t<span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">1.&nbsp;</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\"><strong>音标</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">：课件视频+作业+纠音</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft Yahei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', sans-serif; font-size: 16.3636360168457px; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal;\">\n\t&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft Yahei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', sans-serif; font-size: 16.3636360168457px; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal;\">\n\t&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft Yahei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', sans-serif; font-size: 16.3636360168457px; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal;\">\n\t&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">\n\t<a href=\"http://st.hujiang.com/mag/137101021/\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://i3.s.7.hjfile.cn/entry/201511/7629d928-a7d5-485d-9c72-070b923619c1.bmp\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft Yahei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', sans-serif; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal;\">\n\t<span style=\"font-size: 16.3636360168457px;\">2</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft Yahei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', sans-serif; line-height: 28px;\">. </span><span style=\"font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft Yahei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', sans-serif; line-height: 28px;\"><strong>纠音</strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft Yahei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', sans-serif; line-height: 28px;\">：直播视频+作业+纠音</span></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft Yahei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', sans-serif; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal; text-align: center;\">\n\t<a href=\"http://www.cctalk.com/course/151691927270/\" rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft Yahei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', sans-serif; line-height: 28px;\"><img src=\"http://i3.s.7.hjfile.cn/entry/201511/0e861845-efc8-4476-880a-789383ace438.jpg\" /></span></a></p>\n<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft Yahei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', sans-serif; line-height: 28px; white-space: normal;\">\n\t<span style=\"font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft Yahei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', sans-serif; line-height: 28px;\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft Yahei', 'WenQuanYi Micro Hei', sans-serif; line-height: 28px;\">3</span><span style=\"font-size: 14px; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft Yahei', 'WenQuanYi Micro H